text.__SUMMARY__: Psychotria moseskemei is a species of plant in the family Rubiaceae. It is found in Cameroon and Nigeria. It is threatened by habitat loss.
text.Sources: Cheek, M. & Csiba, L. (2003). "Psychotria moseskemei". The IUCN Red List of Threatened Species. IUCN. 2003: e.T43893A10830527. doi:10.2305/IUCN.UK.2003.RLTS.T43893A10830527.en. Retrieved 19 December 2017.
